        %article.clearfix.segments
          %header
            %h1 Selected Segments
            %p
              Offering mobile services allows our partners to monetize existing assets 
              and make existing products and services more compelling. If you are active 
              in one of the following industries, there is  significant potential in partnering 
              with us to offer mobile telecommunications services. There is also potential 
              beyond these industries, and no limit to the innovation potential of MVNO services!

          %section.span3
            %h2 Retailers
            .vector.bordered 
              %img{src: "img/pic_retailers.svg"}
            %ul
              %li Increase footfall in own points of sales
              %li Improve loyalty of customer base with cross segment/category campaigns
              %li Exploit revenues from mobile services and devices


          %section.span3
            %h2 Ethnic Brands
            .vector.bordered
              %img{src: "img/pic_ethnic_brands.svg"}
            %ul
              %li Monetize international calling routes and customer base
              %li Provide best value mobile service for international calls
              %li Target ethnic groups with individual mobile services


          %section.span3
            %h2 Youth Brands
            .vector.bordered
              %img{src: "img/pic_youth_brands.svg"}
            %ul
              %li Monetize brand awareness and media reach in teenagers and young adults segment
              %li Grow customers' brand interaction time and content consumption
              %li Stimulate brand loyalty

        %article.clearfix.segments

          %section.span3
            %h2 Social Networks
            .vector.bordered
              %img{src: "img/pic_social_networks.svg"}
            %ul
              %li Provide specific price propositions for the mobile social network usage
              %li Monetize user base by adding social commerce and service extras
              %li Encourage user stickiness by integrating mobile services into core of brand proposition

          %section.span3
            %h2 Fixed Operators
            .vector.bordered
              %img{src: "img/pic_fixed_operators.svg"}
