            %h1 MVNO Business Models

          %section
            %p
              We are experienced in large a variety of business models, complementing our 
              partners' assets, competencies and investments. Jointly with our partners, 
              we select the best fitting commercial and technical set-up for each co-operation.

            %p
              Our solution portfolio ranges from brand licensing/branded reselling to national 
              roaming - and includes any model in between. In the first case we operationally 
              manage the whole mobile service delivery and rely on our partners' branding and 
              marketing assets, in the latter case our partner runs an own mobile (core) network.

